        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "It would be really nice to be able to pass a Zend_Filter_Input instance to a form rather than set the validation and filtering on each element. That way the same form can be used with different filter\/validation rules depending on context.\n\nJim Plush has a good write up with a similar concept at:\nhttp:\/\/www.litfuel.net\/plush\/?postid=189\n\nLikewise, it would be good to be able to pass in arrays of validator or filter chains to the form to be applied to the form elements."
        },
